Well this is because of every server nowadays being the exact same thing. Every server has 600+ models and animations, can’t forget they all have the same content. They all have “Perfect Combat”, “Clipped NPC Following”, “Clipped Following”, etc. You get my point, but now just like the time for servers that were spawn pk and extremely fast leveling the remakes get their chance.
